content.rendered:
One of the best hotels in Jogeshwari West, Hotel Baga High Q is a complete budget friendly family Hotel near Andheri, for both Business and Leisure Travelers situated in the heart of Mumbai City. This 3-star budget hotel in Jogeshwari offers 37 spacious rooms.

Hotel Baga High Q, one of the best hotel in Mumbai offers fully air conditioned rooms and is well equiped with best in class modern amenities like LCD TV, free Wi-Fi and much more ……. Our hotel is also well equipped with CCTV surveillance and smoke Fire alarms for safety & Security of our valuable guest. Hotel Baga High Q has an inhouse multi-cuisine restaurant, an Open Air Restaurant with banquet facility and also In house bank facility.
